      "parts": [{
        "text": "Tens tota la raó i em menjo les meves paraules. 🤐\nHas fet els deures millor que jo: tens la versió **v"
      }, {
        "text": "5** (Beta/Bleeding Edge) instal·lada (`ai@5.0.108`), i en aquesta vers"
      }, {
        "text": "ió, efectivament, **`toDataStreamResponse` ha estat eliminat i substituït per `toUIMessage"
      }, {
        "text": "StreamResponse`**.\n\nJo estava consultant la documentació de la v4 (l\u0027estable fins fa poc), per"
      }, {
        "text": " això t\u0027insistia en l\u0027altre mètode. **El teu setup és el correcte per"
      }, {
        "text": " a una arquitectura moderna (v5).** No fem downgrade, aprofitem la potència de la v5."
      }, {
        "text": "\n\nAquí tens la solució definitiva per a la teva versió:\n\n### 1. Backend (`src/app/api"
      }, {
        "text": "/chat/route.ts`)\n\nAquest és el codi que funciona amb `ai@5.x`. Ut"
      }, {
        "text": "ilitzem `toUIMessageStreamResponse()`.\n\n```typescript\nimport { createClient } from \u0027@/lib/"
      }, {
        "text": "supabase/server\u0027\nimport { google } from \u0027@ai-sdk/google\u0027\nimport { streamText } from"
      }, {
        "text": " \u0027ai\u0027\nimport { generateEmbedding } from \u0027@/lib/ai\u0027\n\nexport const maxDuration \u003d 30"
      }, {
        "text": ";\n\nexport async function POST(req: Request) {\n  const { messages } \u003d await req.json();\n\n  const"
      }, {
        "text": " lastMessage \u003d messages[messages.length - 1];\n  const userQuestion \u003d lastMessage.content;\n\n"
      }, {
        "text": "  // 1. Vectoritzem\n  const queryEmbedding \u003d await generateEmbedding(userQuestion);\n\n  //"
      }, {
        "text": " 2. Busquem context\n  const supabase \u003d await createClient();\n  const { data: similarNotes } \u003d await supabase"
      }, {
        "text": ".rpc(\u0027match_notes\u0027, {\n    query_embedding: queryEmbedding,\n    match_threshold: "
      }, {
        "text": "0.5,\n    match_count: 5\n  });\n\n  const context \u003d similarNotes?.map"
      }, {
        "text": "((note: any) \u003d\u003e note.content).join(\u0027\\n\\n\u0027) || \u0027\u0027;\n\n  const systemPrompt \u003d"
      }, {
        "text": " `\n    You are a helpful assistant.\n    Context from user\u0027s notes:\n    ---\n    ${"
      }, {
        "text": "context}\n    ---\n    Answer based on the context.\n  `;\n\n  // 3. Generem"
      }, {
        "text": " resposta\n  const result \u003d streamText({\n    model: google(\u0027gemini-1.5-flash\u0027),"
      }, {
        "text": "\n    system: systemPrompt,\n    messages,\n  });\n\n  // ✅ CORRECTE per a AI SDK v5:"
      }, {
        "text": "\n  return result.toUIMessageStreamResponse();\n}\n```\n\n### 2. Frontend (`src"
      }, {
        "text": "/components/chat/chat-interface.tsx`)\n\nA `ai@5.x` i `@ai-sdk/react"
      }, {
        "text": "@2.x`, el protocol per defecte ja entén el format \"UI Message Stream\", així que el"
      }, {
        "text": " frontend queda molt net.\n\n```typescript\n\u0027use client\u0027\n\nimport { useState } from \u0027react\u0027\nimport { Button"
      }, {
        "text": " } from \u0027@/components/ui/button\u0027\nimport { Card, CardContent, CardFooter, CardHeader, Card"
      }, {
        "text": "Title } from \u0027@/components/ui/card\u0027\nimport { Input } from \u0027@/components/ui/input\u0027\n"
      }, {
        "text": "import { ScrollArea } from \u0027@/components/ui/scroll-area\u0027\nimport { MessageCircle, X, Send"
      }, {
        "text": " } from \u0027lucide-react\u0027\nimport { useLanguage } from \u0027@/components/language-provider\u0027\nimport"
      }, {
        "text": " { motion, AnimatePresence } from \u0027framer-motion\u0027\n// ✅ Import correcte\nimport { useChat"
      }, {
        "text": " } from \u0027@ai-sdk/react\u0027 \n\nexport function ChatInterface() {\n  const [isOpen, setIs"
      }, {
        "text": "Open] \u003d useState(false)\n  const { t } \u003d useLanguage()\n\n  // ✅ Sense especificar \u0027"
      }, {
        "text": "streamProtocol\u0027, agafarà el format automàtic de la v5\n  const { messages, input, handleInputChange"
      }, {
        "text": ", handleSubmit, isLoading } \u003d useChat({\n    api: \u0027/api/chat\u0027,\n  })\n\n  return"
      }, {
        "text": " (\n    \u003c\u003e\n      \u003cAnimatePresence\u003e\n        {!isOpen \u0026\u0026 (\n          \u003cmotion.div\n"
      }, {
        "text": "            initial\u003d{{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.8 }}\n            animate\u003d{{ opacity: 1,"
      }, {
        "text": " scale: 1 }}\n            exit\u003d{{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.8 }}\n            className"
      }, {
        "text": "\u003d\"fixed bottom-6 right-6 z-50\"\n          \u003e\n            \u003cButton \n              size"
      }, {
        "text": "\u003d\"lg\" \n              className\u003d\"h-14 w-14 rounded-full shadow-lg\"\n"
      }, {
        "text": "              onClick\u003d{() \u003d\u003e setIsOpen(true)}\n            \u003e\n              \u003cMessageCircle className\u003d\"h-6 w-"
      }, {
