      "text": "Tens tota la raó. Si el projecte és un \"Segon Cervell amb IA\", la IA no pot ser un *widget* amagat a la cantonada; ha de ser el **copilot**.\n\nProposo transformar l\u0027experiència actual en un **Panell Lateral (Sidebar/Sheet)** complet, similar a com ho fa ChatGPT o Copilot. Això ens permetrà:\n1.  **Més espai:** Veure les respostes llargues còmodament.\n2.  **Historial:** Poder guardar i recuperar converses anteriors.\n3.  **Persistència:** Que si recarregues la pàgina, el xat no desaparegui.\n\nEntrem a la **FASE 6: IA COM A COPILOT (Historial i Sidebar)**.\n\n---\n\n### 💾 Pas 1: La Base de Dades (Historial)\n\nNecessitem guardar les converses. Anem a Supabase -\u003e **SQL Editor** i executem això per crear dues taules noves:\n\n```sql\n-- 1. Taula de Xats (Sessions)\ncreate table chats (\n  id uuid primary key default gen_random_uuid(),\n  user_id uuid references auth.users not null,\n  title text,\n  created_at timestamptz default now()\n);\n\n-- 2. Taula de Missatges\ncreate table messages (\n  id uuid primary key default gen_random_uuid(),\n  chat_id uuid references chats(id) on delete cascade not null,\n  role text not null, -- \u0027user\u0027 o \u0027assistant\u0027\n  content text not null,\n  created_at timestamptz default now()\n);\n\n-- 3. Polítiques de Seguretat (RLS)\nalter table chats enable row level security;\nalter table messages enable row level security;\n\ncreate policy \"Users can view their own chats\" on chats\n  for select using (auth.uid() \u003d user_id);\n\ncreate policy \"Users can insert their own chats\" on chats\n  for insert with check (auth.uid() \u003d user_id);\n\ncreate policy \"Users can delete their own chats\" on chats\n  for delete using (auth.uid() \u003d user_id);\n\ncreate policy \"Users can view messages of their chats\" on messages\n  for select using (\n    exists (select 1 from chats where id \u003d messages.chat_id and user_id \u003d auth.uid())\n  );\n\ncreate policy \"Users can insert messages to their chats\" on messages\n  for insert with check (\n    exists (select 1 from chats where id \u003d messages.chat_id and user_id \u003d auth.uid())\n  );\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🧠 Pas 2: Actualitzar el Backend (`api/chat/route.ts`)\n\nAra, quan la IA respongui, hem de guardar automàticament la conversa a la base de dades.\nEl Vercel AI SDK té una funció màgica anomenada `onFinish` dins de `streamText` per fer justament això.\n\nEdita `src/app/api/chat/route.ts`:\n\n```typescript\nimport { createClient } from \u0027@/lib/supabase/server\u0027\nimport { google } from \u0027@ai-sdk/google\u0027\nimport { streamText, convertToCoreMessages } from \u0027ai\u0027\nimport { generateEmbedding } from \u0027@/lib/ai\u0027\n\nexport const maxDuration \u003d 30;\n\nexport async function POST(req: Request) {\n  // Ara esperem rebre també un \u0027chatId\u0027 (opcional)\n  const { messages, chatId } \u003d await req.json();\n\n  const lastMessage \u003d messages[messages.length - 1];\n  let userQuestion \u003d \u0027\u0027;\n\n  // Extracció del text (igual que abans)\n  if (typeof lastMessage.content \u003d\u003d\u003d \u0027string\u0027) {\n    userQuestion \u003d lastMessage.content;\n  } else if (Array.isArray(lastMessage.parts)) {\n    userQuestion \u003d lastMessage.parts\n      .filter((part: any) \u003d\u003e part.type \u003d\u003d\u003d \u0027text\u0027)\n      .map((part: any) \u003d\u003e part.text)\n      .join(\u0027\\n\u0027);\n  }\n\n  // 1. Embedding + RAG\n  const queryEmbedding \u003d await generateEmbedding(userQuestion);\n  const supabase \u003d await createClient();\n  const { data: similarNotes } \u003d await supabase.rpc(\u0027match_notes\u0027, {\n    query_embedding: queryEmbedding,\n    match_threshold: 0.3,\n    match_count: 5\n  });\n\n  const context \u003d similarNotes?.map((note: any) \u003d\u003e note.content).join(\u0027\\n\\n\u0027) || \u0027\u0027;\n\n  const systemPrompt \u003d `\n    You are a helpful assistant for a \"Second Brain\" app.\n    CONTEXT:\n    ${context}\n    INSTRUCTIONS: Answer based on context. Answer in the user\u0027s language.\n  `;\n\n  // 2. Generar i Guardar\n  const result \u003d streamText({\n    model: google(\u0027gemini-1.5-pro\u0027),\n    system: systemPrompt,\n    messages: convertToCoreMessages(messages),\n    \n    // 🔥 MÀGIA: Guardem a la BD quan acabi de respondre\n    onFinish: async ({ text }) \u003d\u003e {\n      if (!chatId) return; // Si no hi ha ID (mode prova), no guardem\n\n      // Guardem missatge usuari\n      await supabase.from(\u0027messages\u0027).insert({\n        chat_id: chatId,\n        role: \u0027user\u0027,\n        content: userQuestion\n      });\n\n      // Guardem resposta IA\n      await supabase.from(\u0027messages\u0027).insert({\n        chat_id: chatId,\n        role: \u0027assistant\u0027,\n        content: text\n      });\n    }\n  });\n\n  return result.toUIMessageStreamResponse();\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n### 🎨 Pas 3: Nova UI - Panell Lateral (Sheet)\n\nEn lloc d\u0027una targeta petita, usarem el component `Sheet` de Shadcn per fer un sidebar que surti de la dreta.\n\n1.  **Instal·la Sheet:**\n    ```bash\n    npx shadcn@latest add sheet\n    ```\n\n2.  **Crea el nou component `src/components/chat/chat-sidebar.tsx`:**\n    Aquest component gestionarà la llista de xats i la conversa actual.\n\n```typescript\n\u0027use client\u0027\n\nimport { useState, useEffect } from \u0027react\u0027\nimport { Button } from \u0027@/components/ui/button\u0027\nimport { Input } from \u0027@/components/ui/input\u0027\nimport { ScrollArea } from \u0027@/components/ui/scroll-area\u0027\nimport { Sheet, SheetContent, SheetHeader, SheetTitle, SheetTrigger } from \u0027@/components/ui/sheet\u0027\nimport { MessageCircle, Send, Plus, History, Trash2, Bot } from \u0027lucide-react\u0027\nimport { useChat } from \u0027@ai-sdk/react\u0027\nimport ReactMarkdown from \u0027react-markdown\u0027\nimport { createClient } from \u0027@/lib/supabase/client\u0027 // Assegura\u0027t de tenir el client creat\nimport { toast } from \u0027sonner\u0027\nimport { cn } from \u0027@/lib/utils\u0027\n\nexport function ChatSidebar({ userId }: { userId: string }) {\n  const [isOpen, setIsOpen] \u003d useState(false)\n  const [chatId, setChatId] \u003d useState\u003cstring | null\u003e(null)\n  const [chatList, setChatList] \u003d useState\u003cany[]\u003e([])\n  \n  // Supabase client-side per carregar l\u0027historial\n  const supabase \u003d createClient()\n\n  // Hook AI SDK\n  const { messages, input, setInput, append, isLoading, setMessages } \u003d useChat({\n    api: \u0027/api/chat\u0027,\n    body: { chatId }, // Passem l\u0027ID al backend\n    onFinish: () \u003d\u003e {\n        // Opcional: Refrescar llista xats si és nou (per posar-li títol més tard)\n    }\n  })\n\n  // 1. Carregar llista de xats\n  useEffect(() \u003d\u003e {\n    if (isOpen) {\n      const fetchChats \u003d async () \u003d\u003e {\n        const { data } \u003d await supabase.from(\u0027chats\u0027).select(\u0027*\u0027).order(\u0027created_at\u0027, { ascending: false })\n        if (data) setChatList(data)\n      }\n      fetchChats()\n    }\n  }, [isOpen])\n\n  // 2. Carregar missatges d\u0027un xat seleccionat\n  const loadChat \u003d async (id: string) \u003d\u003e {\n    setChatId(id)\n    const { data } \u003d await supabase.from(\u0027messages\u0027).select(\u0027*\u0027).eq(\u0027chat_id\u0027, id).order(\u0027created_at\u0027, { ascending: true })\n    \n    if (data) {\n      // Convertim format DB a format UI\n      const uiMessages \u003d data.map((m: any) \u003d\u003e ({\n        id: m.id,\n        role: m.role,\n        parts: [{ type: \u0027text\u0027, text: m.content }]\n      }))\n      setMessages(uiMessages as any)\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 3. Crear nou xat\n  const createNewChat \u003d async () \u003d\u003e {\n    // Netegem la UI actual\n    setMessages([])\n    setInput(\u0027\u0027)\n    \n    // Creem l\u0027entrada a la DB\n    const { data, error } \u003d await supabase.from(\u0027chats\u0027).insert({\n        user_id: userId,\n        title: \u0027Nova Conversa\u0027\n    }).select().single()\n\n    if (data) {\n        setChatId(data.id)\n        setChatList([data, ...chatList])\n    }\n  }\n\n  // 4. Enviar missatge (Wrapper)\n  const handleSend \u003d async (e?: React.FormEvent) \u003d\u003e {\n    e?.preventDefault()\n    if (!input.trim()) return\n\n    if (!chatId) {\n        await createNewChat()\n        // Esperem un micro-segon perquè l\u0027estat chatId s\u0027actualitzi (react batching) o...\n        // Millor: com que createNewChat és async, podem fer servir el resultat, però per simplicitat MVP:\n        // Si no hi ha chatID, primer el creem, i després enviem.\n        // *Nota: En React pur això pot tenir race conditions, però per l\u0027MVP aguantarà.\n        // L\u0027ideal seria fer el append dins del createNewChat o usar refs.\n    }\n\n    // Enviem\n    await append({\n        role: \u0027user\u0027,\n        content: input\n    })\n    setInput(\u0027\u0027)\n  }\n\n  return (\n    \u003cSheet open\u003d{isOpen} onOpenChange\u003d{setIsOpen}\u003e\n      {/* TRIGGER: El botó flotant gran */}\n      \u003cSheetTrigger asChild\u003e\n        \u003cButton \n            className\u003d\"fixed bottom-8 right-8 h-16 w-16 rounded-full shadow-2xl z-50 transition-transform hover:scale-110\"\n            size\u003d\"icon\"\n        \u003e\n            \u003cBot className\u003d\"h-8 w-8\" /\u003e\n        \u003c/Button\u003e\n      \u003c/SheetTrigger\u003e\n\n      \u003cSheetContent className\u003d\"w-full sm:w-[500px] flex flex-col p-0 gap-0 sm:max-w-[500px]\"\u003e\n        \n        {/* HEADER: Títol + Botó Nou Xat */}\n        \u003cSheetHeader className\u003d\"p-4 border-b bg-muted/20 flex flex-row items-center justify-between space-y-0\"\u003e\n          \u003cSheetTitle className\u003d\"flex items-center gap-2\"\u003e\n            \u003cBot className\u003d\"h-5 w-5 text-primary\" /\u003e\n            Synapse AI\n          \u003c/SheetTitle\u003e\n          \u003cButton variant\u003d\"outline\" size\u003d\"sm\" onClick\u003d{createNewChat}\u003e\n            \u003cPlus className\u003d\"mr-2 h-4 w-4\" /\u003e Nou Xat\n          \u003c/Button\u003e\n        \u003c/SheetHeader\u003e\n\n        \u003cdiv className\u003d\"flex flex-1 overflow-hidden\"\u003e\n            {/* SIDEBAR (Historial) - Només visible si pantalla gran o si volem */}\n            \u003cdiv className\u003d\"w-16 border-r bg-muted/10 flex flex-col items-center py-4 gap-2 overflow-y-auto\"\u003e\n                {chatList.map((chat) \u003d\u003e (\n                    \u003cButton \n                        key\u003d{chat.id} \n                        variant\u003d{chatId \u003d\u003d\u003d chat.id ? \"default\" : \"ghost\"} \n                        size\u003d\"icon\"\n                        className\u003d\"h-10 w-10 rounded-full\"\n                        onClick\u003d{() \u003d\u003e loadChat(chat.id)}\n                        title\u003d{chat.created_at}\n                    \u003e\n                        \u003cHistory className\u003d\"h-4 w-4\" /\u003e\n                    \u003c/Button\u003e\n                ))}\n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            {/* ZONA DE XAT */}\n            \u003cdiv className\u003d\"flex-1 flex flex-col h-full bg-background\"\u003e\n                \u003cScrollArea className\u003d\"flex-1 p-4\"\u003e\n                    {messages.length \u003d\u003d\u003d 0 ? (\n                         \u003cdiv className\u003d\"h-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center p-8 opacity-50\"\u003e\n                            \u003cBot className\u003d\"h-12 w-12 mb-4 text-muted-foreground\" /\u003e\n                            \u003cp className\u003d\"text-lg font-medium\"\u003eCom puc ajudar-te avui?\u003c/p\u003e\n                            \u003cp className\u003d\"text-sm\"\u003ePregunta sobre les teves notes...\u003c/p\u003e\n      